   I See You've Called in Dead: A Novel
   Zibby Publishing

   I See You've Called in Dead, by John Kenney

   It doesn't sound outlandish that a professional obituary writer would
   draft an obituary for himself at one time or another – perhaps even
   featuring a few flattering embellishments, why not? But problems arise
   when said writer – Bud Stanley, the ill-starred hero of Kenney's comic
   novel – drunkenly publishes this whopper-laden exercise in wish
   fulfillment during his own lifetime. Opportunities arise too, though,
   and it's not long before his own death turns his life on its head.
   (BUTTON) Purchase BookI See You’ve Called in Dead by John Kenney
   (BUTTON) close overlay

